AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ACAO_0000029> "Relates an artifact or other material entity to a portion of matter that is part of it and contributes to its characteristic material constitution, without by itself specifying exact composition or quantitative proportion.")
